snippet.title: PS5/ R-Type Final 3 Evolved: Trailer Vol.1
snippet.description:
Here is the first trailer of "R-Type Final 3 Evolved", the shooter game for PlayStation®5.
In addition to the 13 stages and more than 100 player ships included in R-Type Final 2, we've added new features such as launch sequence scenes exclusive to the PS5 version, seven new stages and "My Room".
Please take a look.

- R-Type Final 3 Evolved Official Website:  https://rtypefinal3.com/
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/rtypefinal3_gz 
- EU/NA Region: NIS America, Inc. https://nisamerica.com/games/r-type-final-3-evolved
- AS Region: JUSTDAN https://justdan.com/en/product/published/R-TYPEFINAL3EVOLVED

 #RType #RTypeFinal3Evolved
